# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# zkScatter Testnet Configuration (Sepolia)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# TESTNET only. For LOCAL development use: ./scripts/dev.sh --mock
#
# There are TWO consumers with different env files — keep them separate:
#   • Contract deploy (Foundry)  → contracts/.env   (Section A)
#   • Runtime services (docker)  → ./.env (repo root)(Section B)
# forge auto-loads contracts/.env; docker compose auto-loads root .env.
#
# NOTE: DeploySepolia.s.sol (NOT DeployLocal) is the testnet deploy script.
# DeployLocal is anvil-only — it mints mock tokens and wraps 1100 ETH,
# which reverts on a real chain.

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# SECTION A — Contract deploy   (copy to contracts/.env)
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Run: cd contracts && forge script script/DeploySepolia.s.sol:DeploySepolia \
#        --rpc-url sepolia --broadcast --verify
#      (--rpc-url sepolia → foundry.toml [rpc_endpoints] → SEPOLIA_RPC_URL)

# RPC + verification (Alchemy/Infura). Read via foundry.toml aliases.
SEPOLIA_RPC_URL=https://eth-sepolia.g.alchemy.com/v2/YOUR_KEY
MAINNET_RPC_URL=https://eth-mainnet.g.alchemy.com/v2/YOUR_KEY
ETHERSCAN_API_KEY=YOUR_ETHERSCAN_KEY

# Deployer key — read by the script directly, never on the CLI. gitignored.
# DEDICATED key funded with testnet ETH only. (Or omit and use --account keystore.)
DEPLOYER_KEY=0x...

# Real zk-X509 IdentityRegistry addresses (deployed by the zk-X509 repo's
# Deploy.s.sol with MAX_WALLETS_PER_CERT=10, BEFORE this deploy). REVERT if 0.
SEPOLIA_IDENTITY_REGISTRY=0x...          # User-CA   — gates deposits / claims
SEPOLIA_RELAYER_IDENTITY_REGISTRY=0x...  # Relayer-CA — gates register()

# Owners (multisig recommended; may equal deployer for a quick team testnet).
UPGRADE_OWNER=0x...
TREASURY_ADDRESS=0x...

# Canonical WETH9 (structural PrivateSettlement init param). Verified Sepolia:
SEPOLIA_WETH_ADDRESS=0x7b79995e5f793A07Bc00c21412e50Ecae098E7f9
# MAINNET_WETH_ADDRESS=0xC02aaA39b223FE8D0A0e5C4F27eAD9083C756Cc2

# Optional: external sanctions oracle OR-combined into SanctionsList.
# SANCTIONS_EXTERNAL_ORACLE=0x...

# NOTE: tokens other than WETH are NOT set here. The owner whitelists them
# on-chain AFTER deploy (admin UI / cast setTokenWhitelist on BOTH pool and
# settlement); the frontend reads the live set on-chain via getWhitelistedTokens().
# Verified Sepolia tokens for reference: USDC 0x1c7D4B196Cb0C7B01d743Fbc6116a902379C7238,
# USDT 0x42d3b260c761cd5da022db56fe2f89c4a909b04a, TON 0xa30fe40285b8f5c0457dbc3b7c8a280373c40044

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# SECTION B — Runtime services  (copy to ./.env, repo root)
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Run: docker compose up -d shared-orderbook zk-relayer

# Docker services read RPC_URL (NOT SEPOLIA_RPC_URL). Use the same endpoint.
RPC_URL=https://eth-sepolia.g.alchemy.com/v2/YOUR_KEY

# Contract addresses — fill AFTER deploy (from the summary / deployments/<chainId>.json).
COMMITMENT_POOL_ADDRESS=0x...
PRIVATE_SETTLEMENT_ADDRESS=0x...
FEE_VAULT_ADDRESS=0x...

# Relayer A — dedicated key, minimal gas. Registration is done via the
# operators /register site (KYC -> zk-X509 proof -> admin approval -> bond), not here.
RELAYER_A_KEY=0x...
RELAYER_A_PUBLIC_URL=https://relayer-a.yourdomain.com

# Relayer B (optional, multi-relayer mode)
RELAYER_B_KEY=0x...
RELAYER_B_PUBLIC_URL=https://relayer-b.yourdomain.com

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Frontend (apps/*/.env.local)
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_RPC_URL=https://eth-sepolia.g.alchemy.com/v2/YOUR_KEY
# Token list is read on-chain via getWhitelistedTokens() (#927/#928);
# NEXT_PUBLIC_TOKENS is only an optional metadata/label fallback.
